00:12:36.480 --> 00:12:39.921
wonderful thing in the British
Parliament where they ask the

00:12:39.921 --> 00:12:42.779
Prime Minister
questions--obnoxious questions.

00:12:42.779 --> 00:12:45.987
And when they start getting too
