00:12:48.722 --> 00:12:51.680
say, "I refer the Honorable
Gentleman to the answer I gave

00:12:51.680 --> 00:12:54.391
some moments ago."
So, if you're going to ask what

00:12:54.391 --> 00:12:57.478
